overview: Spend a Late Night in with Alan and Justin as they show you their favourite unseen clips and funniest bits from the Friday & Sunday Night Project. Featuring, for the first time ever, top celebrities from the show as you’ve never seen them before, plus extended clips and outtakes that couldn't be shown on TV. All this introduced by showbiz's number 1 golden couple as they spend their own Late Night…in bed together! Good times!
title: The Sunday Late Night Project
